headline: Is Tractor Supply (TSCO) Pricing Reflect Longer Term Rural Spending Story After Recent Share Pullback
summary: If you are wondering whether Tractor Supply's share price still lines up with the value of the business, this article walks you through what the current numbers might be telling you. Recently, the stock has been mixed, with a 7% decline over the last 7 days, a 1.7% gain over 30 days, and returns of 0.1% year to date, plus 17.3% over 3 years and 82.2% over 5 years.
